<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>DebSwims</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=clash-display@400,500,600,700&display=swap">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    /* Hokusai Great Wave palette */
    --prussian:      #1B3A6B;
    --prussian-deep: #0D2240;
    --prussian-mid:  #2B5499;
    --wave-blue:     #2E6DB4;
    --foam:          #EEF4F8;
    --foam-white:    #F8FBFD;
    --cream:         #F5EED8;
    --cream-dark:    #E8D9B0;
    --ink:           #0A1628;
    --text-mid:      #3A5478;
    --text-light:    #7A96B8;
    --radius:        14px;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    background: var(--foam-white);
    color: var(--ink);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.1rem 5%;
    background: rgba(248,251,253,0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27,58,107,0.13);
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  header.scrolled { box-shadow: 0 2px 18px rgba(27,58,107,0.10); }

  .logo {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--prussian-deep);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .logo span { color: var(--wave-blue); }

  nav { display: flex; gap: 1.6rem; }

  nav a {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  nav a:hover { color: var(--prussian); }

  .cta-btn {
    background: var(--prussian);
    color: var(--foam-white);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(27,58,107,0.25);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    background: var(--prussian-deep);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(27,58,107,0.35);
  }

  .cta-btn.outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid rgba(238,244,248,0.6);
    color: var(--foam);
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .cta-btn.outline:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 7rem 5% 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--prussian-deep);
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505118380757-91f5f5632de0?w=1600&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 60%;
    opacity: 0.28;
    z-index: 0;
    filter: saturate(0.5) hue-rotate(195deg);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.90) 40%, rgba(13,34,64,0.25) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content { max-width: 680px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(46,109,180,0.25);
    color: var(--foam);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(238,244,248,0.25);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.13;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(25px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.35s forwards;
  }

  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--cream); }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.13rem;
    color: rgba(238,244,248,0.80);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(25px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .hero-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(25px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.65s forwards;
  }

  .hero-wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 90px;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-wave svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; }

  /* ── FEATURES ── */
  .features { background: var(--foam-white); padding: 5.5rem 5%; }

  .section-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--wave-blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--prussian-deep);
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.8rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--foam-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem;
    border: 1.5px solid #8AACB8;
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    height: 100%;
  }

  .feature-card.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease, box-shadow 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(27,58,107,0.12);
    border-color: var(--prussian-mid);
  }

  .feature-icon { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; display: block; }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--prussian-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── WAVE STRIP ── */
  .wave-strip {
    width: 100%;
    height: 260px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
  }

  .wave-strip img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 40%;
    display: block;
    filter: saturate(0.6) hue-rotate(185deg) brightness(0.8);
  }

  .wave-strip-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
      rgba(13,34,64,0.2) 0%,
      rgba(13,34,64,0.0) 40%,
      rgba(248,251,253,0.75) 100%);
  }

  /* ── POOL JOURNAL FORM ── */
  .pool-section { padding: 5rem 5%; background: var(--foam-white); }

  .pool-form-wrap {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--prussian);
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) * 1.4);
    padding: 3rem 2.8rem;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--prussian-mid);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(27,58,107,0.20);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .pool-form-wrap .form-section-heading,
  .pool-form-wrap .form-group label,
  .pool-form-wrap .upload-text,
  .pool-form-wrap .upload-text strong { color: var(--foam) !important; }

  .pool-form-wrap .form-divider { border-top-color: rgba(238,244,248,0.2); }

  .pool-form-wrap .photo-upload-area {
    border-color: rgba(238,244,248,0.35);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .pool-form-wrap .photo-upload-area:hover {
    border-color: var(--foam);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }

  .pool-form-wrap.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.2rem; }

  .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.3rem; }

  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group textarea,
  .form-group select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1.5px solid #8AACB8;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: #ffffff;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    outline: none;
    resize: vertical;
    appearance: none;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus,
  .form-group select:focus {
    border-color: var(--prussian);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(27,58,107,0.10);
    background: #fff;
  }

  .form-group textarea { min-height: 110px; }

  .photo-upload-area {
    border: 2px dashed rgba(27,58,107,0.25);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    background: var(--foam-white);
    position: relative;
  }

  .photo-upload-area:hover, .photo-upload-area.dragover {
    border-color: var(--prussian);
    background: rgba(27,58,107,0.04);
  }

  .photo-upload-area input[type="file"] {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    background: none;
  }

  .photo-upload-area input[type="file"]:focus { box-shadow: none; }

  .upload-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block; }

  .upload-text { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .upload-text strong { color: var(--prussian); }

  .photo-previews {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(100px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.7rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .photo-preview-item {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--cream-dark);
  }

  .photo-preview-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }

  .photo-preview-item .remove-photo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 4px; right: 4px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .photo-preview-item .remove-photo:hover { background: rgba(200,0,0,0.8); }

  .stars { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }

  .star {
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--cream-dark);
    transition: color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .star:hover, .star.active { color: var(--prussian); transform: scale(1.15); }

  .form-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
    margin: 1.8rem 0;
  }

  .form-section-heading {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--prussian-deep);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .submit-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.95rem;
    background: var(--prussian);
    color: var(--foam-white);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(27,58,107,0.28);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .submit-btn:hover {
    background: var(--prussian-deep);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(27,58,107,0.38);
  }

  .success-msg {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(27,58,107,0.08);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--prussian);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ── POOL ENTRIES ── */
  .entries-section { padding: 0 5% 5rem; background: var(--foam-white); }

  .entries-grid {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .entry-card {
    background: var(--foam-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1.5px solid #8AACB8;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(27,58,107,0.07);
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease forwards;
  }

  .entry-photos { display: flex; gap: 4px; max-height: 200px; overflow: hidden; }

  .entry-photos img {
    flex: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    height: 200px;
    min-width: 0;
    filter: saturate(0.85);
  }

  .entry-body { padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem; }

  .entry-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .entry-pool-name {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--prussian-deep);
  }

  .entry-date { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-light); }

  .entry-stars { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--prussian); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

  .entry-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .entry-tips {
    background: rgba(27,58,107,0.07);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--prussian-deep);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .entry-tips strong { font-weight: 500; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }

  .entry-website {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 0.87rem;
    color: var(--wave-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .entry-website:hover { color: var(--prussian-deep); text-decoration: underline; }

  .no-entries {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--prussian-deep);
    color: rgba(238,244,248,0.5);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 5%;
    font-size: 0.87rem;
  }

  footer .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--foam);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding-top: 6rem; }
    .pool-form-wrap { padding: 2rem 1.4rem; }
    .features-grid, .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header id="site-header">
  <div class="logo">Deb<span>Swims</span></div>
  <nav>
    <a href="#features">About</a>
    <a href="#entries-section">Pool Reviews</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="hero-tag">🌊 My H2O Journey</span>
    <h1>Exploring H2O, <em>One Pool, Lake & Ocean at a Time</em></h1>
    <p>Welcome to my personal swim and water body journal — where I share reviews, tips, and photos from every pool, lake, ocean, and water body I've had the pleasure (or adventure) of swimming in or visiting.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#features" class="cta-btn">About This Site</a>
      <a href="#entries-section" class="cta-btn outline">Browse H2O Reviews</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 90" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,45 C180,90 360,10 540,50 C720,90 900,20 1080,55 C1260,90 1380,30 1440,45 L1440,90 L0,90Z" fill="#F8FBFD"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <p class="section-label">What You'll Find Here</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">My Personal H2O Diary</h2>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <span class="feature-icon">
        <svg width="48" height="42" viewBox="0 0 48 42" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <!-- Water surface ripple -->
          <path d="M2 28 C7 23, 13 21, 18 25 C23 29, 29 25, 34 20 C38 17, 44 19, 46 19" stroke="#2E6DB4" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" opacity="0.45"/>
          <path d="M2 34 C8 29, 14 27, 20 31 C26 35, 32 30, 38 25 C41 22, 44 24, 46 24" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" opacity="0.3"/>
          <!-- Goggle strap -->
          <path d="M13 16 C13 16, 10 15, 7 16" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M35 16 C35 16, 38 15, 41 16" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <!-- Bridge between lenses -->
          <path d="M22 16 Q24 14 26 16" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
          <!-- Left lens -->
          <ellipse cx="16" cy="17" rx="7" ry="6" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="2"/>
          <ellipse cx="16" cy="17" rx="4.5" ry="4" fill="#2E6DB4" opacity="0.35"/>
          <circle cx="13.5" cy="14.5" r="1.2" fill="white" opacity="0.7"/>
          <!-- Right lens -->
          <ellipse cx="32" cy="17" rx="7" ry="6" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="2"/>
          <ellipse cx="32" cy="17" rx="4.5" ry="4" fill="#2E6DB4" opacity="0.35"/>
          <circle cx="29.5" cy="14.5" r="1.2" fill="white" opacity="0.7"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <h3>Swimming</h3>
      <p>Learn what it's like to swim at this H2O body, how many lanes there are in the pool, what the waves are like in this ocean, and what the overall vibe is. Get tips and advice about swimming there.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <span class="feature-icon">
        <svg width="48" height="44" viewBox="0 0 48 44" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <!-- Lane line 1 -->
          <rect x="2"  y="10" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#2E6DB4"/>
          <rect x="9"  y="10" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#2E6DB4" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="16" y="10" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#2E6DB4"/>
          <rect x="23" y="10" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#2E6DB4" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="30" y="10" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#2E6DB4"/>
          <rect x="37" y="10" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#2E6DB4" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="2" y1="12.5" x2="42" y2="12.5" stroke="#2E6DB4" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>

          <!-- Lane line 2 -->
          <rect x="2"  y="20" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="9"  y="20" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#1B3A6B"/>
          <rect x="16" y="20" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#EEF4F8" stroke="#1B3A6B" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="23" y="20" width="5" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="#1B3A6B"/>
